<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Coin pendant【Third-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_CoinsPendant.label>铜钱吊坠【三品】</RI_Talisman_CoinsPendant.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Third-rate】Talisman.\n\nA red rope pendant with coins. The design source of the coin pendant is heard to be an ancient Taoist school handed down the talisman. They imprinted a kind of body protection exercises and spiritual stones called golden mantra on specially treated copper coins, so that ordinary people wearing copper coins can temporarily use a small part of the power of the body protection gold. After many years of iteration and upgrading, coin pendants have become synonymous with cheap shields, and are loved by many free-cultivators. -->
  <RI_Talisman_CoinsPendant.description>【三品】法宝\n\n一枚绑着铜钱的红绳吊坠。铜钱吊坠的设计来源，听说是一支古老的道士门派流传下来的护身法宝。他们将一种被称为金光咒的护体功法和灵石，刻印在经过特殊处理的铜钱上，从而让佩戴铜钱的凡人，都能暂时使出护体金光的一小部分威能。\n\n之后经过不知多少年的迭代和升级，铜钱吊坠已经成为了廉价护盾的代名词，被诸多散修所钟爱。</RI_Talisman_CoinsPendant.description>
  <!-- EN: flare -->
  <RI_Talisman_CoinsPendant.comps.CompApparelReloadable.chargeNoun>释放</RI_Talisman_CoinsPendant.comps.CompApparelReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
  <RI_Talisman_CoinsPendant.comps.CompApparelReloadable.cooldownGerund>冷却中</RI_Talisman_CoinsPendant.comps.CompApparelReloadable.cooldownGerund>
  <!-- EN: Golden shield -->
  <RI_Talisman_CoinsPendant.verbs.Golden_shield.label>金光护体</RI_Talisman_CoinsPendant.verbs.Golden_shield.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Fire pearl【Second-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_Firefighter.label>避火珠【二品】</RI_Talisman_Firefighter.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Second-rate】Talisman.\n\nA fiery red pearl, look carefully can find a flame pattern in its beating, radiating warmth. The pearl makes the wearer immune to the flame. -->
  <RI_Talisman_Firefighter.description>【二品】法宝\n\n一颗火红色的宝珠，仔细看能发现有烈焰花纹在其内跳动，散发温暖。这颗宝珠可以令佩戴者免疫火焰。</RI_Talisman_Firefighter.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Golden bowl【First-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl.label>金钵【一品】</RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl.label>
  <!-- EN: 【First-rate】Talisman.\n\nA bowl made of pure gold covered with pattern and fine engraving, gently tapped, you can hear the sound of waves coming from the bowl. The shock wave produced by the knock of the gold bowl can hold people in place, which is a very powerful talisman. -->
  <RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl.description>【一品】法宝\n\n一个布满了锤纹和精细刻印的纯金打造的钵，轻轻敲击，凑近就能听到来自钵中的浪涛声。金钵敲击产生的冲击波可以将人定在原地，是一种十分强大的法宝。</RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl.description>
  <!-- EN: flare -->
  <RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl.comps.CompApparelReloadable.chargeNoun>释放</RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl.comps.CompApparelReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
  <RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl.comps.CompApparelReloadable.cooldownGerund>冷却中</RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl.comps.CompApparelReloadable.cooldownGerund>
  <!-- EN: Golden Mantra -->
  <RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl.verbs.Golden_Mantra.label>定身金咒</RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl.verbs.Golden_Mantra.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Golden bowl field -->
  <RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl_Bullet.label>定身领域</RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl_Bullet.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Golden bowl field -->
  <RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl_Shield.label>定身领域</RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl_Shield.label>
  <!-- EN: Golden bowl field. -->
  <RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl_Shield.description>定身领域</RI_Talisman_GoldenBowl_Shield.description>
