  <!-- EN: Medical gourd【Second-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_Greengourd.label>青囊葫芦【二品】</RI_Talisman_Greengourd.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Second-rate】Talisman.\n\nA smooth jade green gourd, with a light medicinal fragrance. The gourd can enhance the wearer's medical skills. -->
  <RI_Talisman_Greengourd.description>【二品】法宝\n\n一座光滑如玉的青色葫芦，带有一股淡淡药香。这颗葫芦可以令佩戴者的医术更加精进。</RI_Talisman_Greengourd.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Immortal-binding rope【First-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_ImmortalBindingRope.label>捆仙绳【一品】</RI_Talisman_ImmortalBindingRope.label>
  <!-- EN: 【First-rate】Talisman.\n\nA stretch of gold wire about three meters long, emitting a light gold. This magical rope can bind any creature and force it to the ground. -->
  <RI_Talisman_ImmortalBindingRope.description>【一品】法宝\n\n一段展开大约有3米长的金丝绳，散发出淡淡的金光。这条神奇的绳子可以捆住任何生物，并且令它们强行倒地。</RI_Talisman_ImmortalBindingRope.description>
  <!-- EN: flare -->
  <RI_Talisman_ImmortalBindingRope.comps.CompApparelReloadable.chargeNoun>释放</RI_Talisman_ImmortalBindingRope.comps.CompApparelReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
  <RI_Talisman_ImmortalBindingRope.comps.CompApparelReloadable.cooldownGerund>冷却中</RI_Talisman_ImmortalBindingRope.comps.CompApparelReloadable.cooldownGerund>
  <!-- EN: Immortal-binding rope -->
  <RI_Talisman_ImmortalBindingRope.verbs.Immortalbinding_rope.label>捆仙绳</RI_Talisman_ImmortalBindingRope.verbs.Immortalbinding_rope.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Jade Ruyi【Third-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_JadeRuyi.label>玉如意【三品】</RI_Talisman_JadeRuyi.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Third-rate】Talisman.\n\nJade production of Ruyi. Wearing it on the body can provide some healing effects, but the Ruyi itself is more delicate and needs to be avoided. -->
  <RI_Talisman_JadeRuyi.description>【三品】法宝\n\n用翡翠制作的如意。佩戴在身上可以提供一些治愈的效果，但是法宝本身比较娇贵，需要避免磕碰。</RI_Talisman_JadeRuyi.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Poly stone tower【Second-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_PolyStoneTower.label>聚石塔【二品】</RI_Talisman_PolyStoneTower.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Second-rate】Talisman.\n\nA heavy stone tower, unattractive, even some cracks above.When the wearer holds the stone tower tightly, a powerful shock wave is unleashed. -->
  <RI_Talisman_PolyStoneTower.description>【二品】法宝\n\n一台有些沉重的石塔，其貌不扬，上面甚至有些裂缝。当佩戴者紧紧握住石塔，就会激发出一阵强大的冲击波。</RI_Talisman_PolyStoneTower.description>
  <!-- EN: flare -->
  <RI_Talisman_PolyStoneTower.comps.CompApparelReloadable.chargeNoun>释放</RI_Talisman_PolyStoneTower.comps.CompApparelReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
  <RI_Talisman_PolyStoneTower.comps.CompApparelReloadable.cooldownGerund>冷却中</RI_Talisman_PolyStoneTower.comps.CompApparelReloadable.cooldownGerund>
  <!-- EN: Flying sand and stone -->
  <RI_Talisman_PolyStoneTower.verbs.Flying_sand_and_stone.label>飞沙走石</RI_Talisman_PolyStoneTower.verbs.Flying_sand_and_stone.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Purple golden gourd【First-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_PurpleGoldenGourd.label>紫金葫芦【一品】</RI_Talisman_PurpleGoldenGourd.label>
  <!-- EN: 【First-rate】Talisman.\n\nA gourd made of metal cast and tempered, carved with strange patterns, it feels like the eye is sucked into it. It is said to be a weapon invented by a celestial being to use against his own kind. There are also rumors that someone once found a long-buried purple and gold gourd in some ancient ruins, and released the ancient people held in it. -->
  <RI_Talisman_PurpleGoldenGourd.description>【一品】法宝\n\n一尊由金属铸造锤炼而成的葫芦，上面雕刻着奇异的花纹，令人觉得视线都要被吸入其中。据说这是一位天仙发明出来的武器，专门用来对付同类。还有传言，有人曾在一些古代遗迹中找到尘封已久的紫金葫芦，并放出了其中关押的古人。</RI_Talisman_PurpleGoldenGourd.description>
  
  <!-- EN: QianKun bag【First-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_QiankunStorageBag.label>乾坤袋【一品】</RI_Talisman_QiankunStorageBag.label>
  <!-- EN: 【First-rate】Talisman.\n\nA pocket made of a rather soft material.This is an upgraded version of the storage bag, because of its gorgeous appearance and very easy to use ability, it is called by some practitioners as a necessity for advanced practitioners. -->
  <RI_Talisman_QiankunStorageBag.description>【一品】法宝\n\n用一种相当柔软的面料制作而成的口袋。这是储物袋的升级版，因为其华丽的外表和十分好用的能力，被一部分修炼者称为高级修炼者必需品。</RI_Talisman_QiankunStorageBag.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Wooden token【Third-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_SandalwoodToken.label>木制令牌【三品】</RI_Talisman_SandalwoodToken.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Third-rate】Talisman.\n\nThe antique bell emits a green light and, when shaken, gives the impression of being spied upon by its eyes. It exudes a unique Qi that is impervious to even the deadliest poisons. -->
  <RI_Talisman_SandalwoodToken.description>【三品】法宝\n\n一枚散发着木香的令牌，正面用朱砂染上了符咒。可以略微幻化佩戴者的面容，看上去更吸引人。</RI_Talisman_SandalwoodToken.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Storage bag【Second-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_StorageBag.label>储物袋【二品】</RI_Talisman_StorageBag.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Second-rate】Talisman.\n\nAlthough unverifiable by reliable sources, this enchanted tool is widely recognized for its exceptional utility. Its remarkable capacity to hold much more than its own volume attracts numerous practitioners seeking its benefits. Contrary to popular belief, any storage device functions not as an interdimensional conduit but rather as a key unlocking access to specific repositories. Each container corresponds uniquely with an individual repository situated within an eternal spatial realm. According to legend, there exists a microcosm fashioned by celestial beings specifically designed for storing personal effects—referred colloquially as 'the black box world'. Rumors suggest that this enigmatic realm may even possess something akin to managerial oversight over these repositories; should complications arise due to commingling within them necessitating intervention or clearance procedures—individuals have recourse through destruction of their magical receptacle followed by complete evacuation of their repository contents if required—all powered endlessly via what's purportedly sourced from wormhole cores within 'the black box world'." -->
  <RI_Talisman_StorageBag.description>【二品】法宝\n\n须弥藏芥子，芥子纳须弥。\n\n这种神奇的法宝，来源已经无法考证，人们只知道这是一种极其好用的随身法宝。其能容纳远远超过本身体积的特性，令无数修炼者趋之若鹜。\n\n任何储物法宝其原理，并非是一个联通两方世界的通道，而是一把打开特定仓库的锁。每个储物袋都会链接到一个独一无二的仓库，而所有的仓库都位于太空中的一处永恒之地。传说那里是天仙创造出来，用于存放个人物品的一方小世界，也被称为“黑箱界”，还有流言声称，黑箱界至今还有类似于仓库管理员的角色存在，为了应对仓库混用，储物法宝被毁，仓库需要清空等问题。而为储物袋提供无限能量，从而能打开虫洞的源头，据说也正是维持黑箱界运转的核心。</RI_Talisman_StorageBag.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Three king tower【First-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_ThreeKingTower.label>三王玲珑塔【一品】</RI_Talisman_ThreeKingTower.label>
  <!-- EN: 【First-rate】Talisman.\n\nA gold-plated tower refracts a colorful light, from different angles to see the past, can see its brilliant changing colors.When the wearer holds the tower in his hand, a strong shield is created to protect the wearer. -->
  <RI_Talisman_ThreeKingTower.description>【一品】法宝\n\n一尊折射出七彩光芒的镀金宝塔，从不同角度看过去，能看见其绚丽变幻的颜色。当佩戴者将宝塔端在手上时，将会产生一层强大的护盾，保护佩戴者。</RI_Talisman_ThreeKingTower.description>
  <!-- EN: flare -->
  <RI_Talisman_ThreeKingTower.comps.CompApparelReloadable.chargeNoun>释放</RI_Talisman_ThreeKingTower.comps.CompApparelReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
  <RI_Talisman_ThreeKingTower.comps.CompApparelReloadable.cooldownGerund>冷却中</RI_Talisman_ThreeKingTower.comps.CompApparelReloadable.cooldownGerund>
  <!-- EN: Three king shield -->
  <RI_Talisman_ThreeKingTower.verbs.Three_king_shield.label>三王护体</RI_Talisman_ThreeKingTower.verbs.Three_king_shield.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Toxic bell【Third-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_ToxicBell.label>驱毒铃【三品】</RI_Talisman_ToxicBell.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Third-rate】Talisman.\n\nAn antique, emitting green light of the bell, shaking the bell can feel, as if from the eyes of the bell spy. This bell can emit a special Qi, a hundred poison can not be penetrated. -->
  <RI_Talisman_ToxicBell.description>【三品】法宝\n\n一颗古色古香，散发着青色幽光的铃铛，晃动铃铛便能感受到，仿佛来自铃铛的目光窥探。这枚铃铛可以散发出特殊的灵气，令人百毒不侵。</RI_Talisman_ToxicBell.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Tusk pendant【Third-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_TuskPendant.label>象牙项链【三品】</RI_Talisman_TuskPendant.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Third-rate】Talisman.\n\nAn tusk pendant with copper hoops and covered with finely carved ornamentations made a slight whimper as the wind blew through its crevices. This pendant allows the wearer to move faster than normal. -->
  <RI_Talisman_TuskPendant.description>【三品】法宝\n\n一条镶嵌着铜箍的象牙项链，表面布满精雕细琢的纹饰，当风吹过其上的缝隙时，有轻微的呜咽声响起。这枚项链可以使佩戴者的速度超出常人。</RI_Talisman_TuskPendant.description>
  
  <!-- EN: White jade vase【First-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_WhiteJadeVase.label>白玉瓶【一品】</RI_Talisman_WhiteJadeVase.label>
  <!-- EN: 【First-rate】Talisman.\n\nA white jade vase, reinforced and carved with turquoise, seems to contain a never-ending supply of healing liquid. -->
  <RI_Talisman_WhiteJadeVase.description>【一品】法宝\n\n一尊通体乳白色的玉瓶，用绿松石加固和雕饰，其内似乎有永远也倒不完的疗愈液体。</RI_Talisman_WhiteJadeVase.description>
  <!-- EN: flare -->
