  <!-- EN: Wind ring【Second-rate】 -->
  <RI_Talisman_WindRing.label>风戒【二品】</RI_Talisman_WindRing.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Second-rate】Talisman.\n\nA ring of silver, engraved with stately lines, and set with a red stone in the middle. This small ring can emit a powerful wind, only the wearer will not be affected. -->
  <RI_Talisman_WindRing.description>【二品】法宝\n\n一枚白银铸就的戒指，其上雕刻着庄严的纹路，并在正中镶嵌了一颗红石。这颗小小的戒指能散发强大的狂风，只有佩戴者不会受到影响。</RI_Talisman_WindRing.description>
